\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 07, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104iyk1665702722035.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/iyk1665702722035.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/iyk1665702722035.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"iyk1665702722035\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Swap the normal meaning of the profile characters with the literal\n      characters.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"iyk1665702722035__topic_d143288e1_d143289e1_d143290e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iyk1665702722035__p_d143291e1_d143292e1_d143293e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$SWAP_GOLD_PROFILES</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iyk1665702722035__section_l2k_jcz_kwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d629203e59\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"iyk1665702722035__table_d17042e1_d17043e1_d17044e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Any application assignment file </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[SETTINGS]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iyk1665702722035__section_fbx_lcz_kwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d629203e105\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iyk1665702722035__p_d143300e1_d143301e1_d143302e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$SWAP_GOLD_PROFILES</span> swaps the\n            normal meaning of the profile characters (GOLD *,GOLD &amp;, GOLD |, GOLD &lt;, GOLD\n            &gt;, GOLD ?, GOLD =, GOLD !) with the corresponding literal characters (*, &amp;, |,\n            &lt;, &gt;, ?, =, !).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iyk1665702722035__p_d143303e1_d143304e1_d143305e1\">When <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$SWAP_GOLD_PROFILES</span> is\n            present, to enter a profile that matches 0-n characters, you need to enter only\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">*</code>. To enter the literal character <code class=\"ph codeph\">*</code>, you then need\n            to enter GOLD *.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"iyk1665702722035__note_jdt_ncz_kwb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$SWAP_GOLD_PROFILES</span> does not\n            affect the subfield separator character.</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528759\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528759\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$SWAP_GOLD_PROFILES Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 07, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Swap the normal meaning of the profile characters with the literal characters. $SWAP_GOLD_PROFILES Defaults Assignment file: Any application assignment file Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: None Description $SWAP_GOLD_PROFILES swaps the normal meaning of the profile characters (GOLD *,GOLD &, GOLD |, GOLD <, GOLD >, GOLD ?, GOLD =, GOLD !) with the corresponding literal characters (*, &, |, <, >, ?, =, !). When $SWAP_GOLD_PROFILES is present, to enter a profile that matches 0-n characters, you need to enter only * . To enter the literal character * , you then need to enter GOLD *. Note: $SWAP_GOLD_PROFILES does not affect the subfield separator character. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}